":1776434,"uid":333301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T23:09:00.000Z","msg":"成日都覺得5.1果種好神奇<br />\n宜家8D聽完差啲高潮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"6b1e4666543db57163971773501342452f9a7c91","tid":1776434,"uid":560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T12:21:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=a9n4XBrr_FE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Da9n4XBrr_FE&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2Fz2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=97c76256\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=a9n4XBrr_FE</a><br />\nlike this?"}}